<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Click <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Write off</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="78">Click <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="78">OK</strong>.</li>
